description:
This skill is for the League game. It lets you ask what are the skills of the champion you want to know.

For example, you can ask Alexa for the skills of Ashe by saying:
* Alexa, ask League Champion what is skill of Ashe
* Alexa, ask League Champion what are skills of Ashe
* Alexa, ask League Champion skill of Ashe
* Alexa, ask League Champion for Ashe skill
* Alexa, ask League Champion for Ashe
Then, Alexa will tell you Ashe's passive, Q, W, E, and R skill.

This might help you to understand ally and enemy champ during loading. Good luck! ;)
